**Horsemen** | Ability Set
Passive: Emit `ApocalypseCheck`
On `ApocalypseCheck` Emitted: Role Change @Self to `Apocalyptic Horseman` [Condition: (not (@(Align:!Horsemen,Class:!Unaligned,Attr:!Doomed) exists)) and (not (@(Align:Horsemen,Group:!Horsemen) exists)) and (@Self->Role is not `Apocalyptic Horseman`)]
On Death: Remove `Doomed` from @All [Condition: not (@(Align:Horsemen) exists)]
